text: Ataxocerithium huttoni is a species of medium-sized sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Cerithiidae. ==References== == Further reading == * Powell A W B, William Collins Publishers Ltd, Auckland 1979 Category:Cerithiidae Category:Gastropods of New Zealand Category:Gastropods described in 1895
title: Ataxocerithium huttoni
